Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.03,0:01:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want to close the Wellington\NCoal Mine and stop the work!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.07,0:01:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.64,0:01:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,In this way I have to pay the mine workers
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.92,0:01:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,the usual salaries!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.24,0:01:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course you have to take responsibility!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.93,0:01:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to give me your most precious thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.58,0:01:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to give me Lassie for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.67,0:01:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,As I said exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.32,0:01:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And when the coal comes out,\NI will give you Lassie back!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.97,0:01:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But, if not...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.95,0:01:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lassie will be mine!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.97,0:01:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.18,0:02:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you trust your father so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.84,0:02:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.74,0:02:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.61,0:02:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure the coal will come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.39,0:02:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I will regain Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.51,0:02:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.87,0:02:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.96,0:02:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,DO YOUR BEST, JOHN, AND PROTECT LASSIE!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.10,0:02:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.10,0:02:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, good morning John! I already ate!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.08,0:02:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Father haven't returned since yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.34,0:02:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.66,0:02:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I've returned after you fall asleep last night!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.75,0:02:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But John grew up a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.70,0:02:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You still have Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.36,0:02:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Always...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.16,0:02:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.64,0:02:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go to work now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.32,0:02:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave the rest to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.23,0:03:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.26,0:03:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.07,0:03:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.45,0:03:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stay alone anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.47,0:03:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.60,0:03:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,After school I'll go to the mine, won't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.58,0:03:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Who were you talking to exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.13,0:03:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.45,0:03:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.63,0:03:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As I expected here!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.28,0:03:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Bad, how long is it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.80,0:03:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the tenth!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.45,0:03:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as the tenth indicates\Nthat I have grown a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.42,0:03:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Go home and sleep, you didn't left last night!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.21,0:03:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.49,0:04:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There are a lot of things I have to do here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.16,0:04:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough, Sam, I've received
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.06,0:04:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,another report from the Duke!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.43,0:04:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.55,0:04:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he would postpone\Nthe closure of the mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.61,0:04:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You can now continue\Nto investigate this matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.03,0:04:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,O-oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.55,0:04:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The owner will pay for these things!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.32,0:04:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,He will also pay salaries to all, as usual!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.68,0:04:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But the talk that I had with him...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.12,0:04:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Sam? Shouldn't you rejoice now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.54,0:04:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure the pressure is not on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.97,0:04:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.00,0:04:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,However, what makes the wind\Nsuddenly change its way?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.64,0:04:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't bother about it now!\NThank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.37,0:04:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wait a little here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.33,0:04:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.43,0:04:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.09,0:04:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, be silent!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.41,0:04:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,- How long will you keep barking like this?\N{\i1}- Lassie!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.79,0:04:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is it in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.58,0:04:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You should be ashamed of what you did!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.13,0:04:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.66,0:05:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.25,0:05:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You talked to my son
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.47,0:05:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,to take the dog that he cared so much for!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.46,0:05:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is a very cowardly act!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.46,0:05:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Sam, calm down! Sam...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.17,0:05:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That boy is very conscious,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.48,0:05:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,and doesn't do such foolish things!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.98,0:05:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Also John, as a man, made a promise to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.17,0:05:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, as a man?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.94,0:05:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He's only 11 years old!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.35,0:05:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.94,0:05:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you trust your son's word?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.33,0:05:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Or don't you trust yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.24,0:05:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.87,0:05:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,John trusts you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.79,0:05:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He still thinks that coal will come out
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.25,0:05:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,exactly as you told him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.67,0:05:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Your son has agreed, because\Nhe trusts you, Mr. Carraclough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.86,0:06:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you understand the calculation?\N2 multiply by 4 equals 8!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.09,0:06:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,4 multiply by 5 equals 20,\Nand 4 multiply by 1 equals 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.21,0:06:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,xxx
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.05,0:06:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.90,0:06:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Today is John acting strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.48,0:06:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,John...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.83,0:06:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all we studied for today!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.56,0:06:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,John Carraclough!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.95,0:06:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}John Carraclough!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.53,0:06:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.52,0:06:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Today you should listen like the other\Nchildren and gather information!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.11,0:06:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-y-yes... i-i-information?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.81,0:06:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.85,0:06:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Carraclough!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.96,0:06:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Throughout the day you thought to other things!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.85,0:06:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.77,0:06:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,In this case, you'll see!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.87,0:06:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie will laugh at you when it salutes you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.69,0:07:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.53,0:07:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie came here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.63,0:07:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.73,0:07:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,John!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.90,0:07:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.11,0:07:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.48,0:07:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.81,0:07:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.04,0:07:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you come back, Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.18,0:07:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Later on we'll talk with the Duke.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.77,0:07:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, you are here as I expected!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.43,0:07:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You have been well trained how\Nto escape quickly, it's so stunning!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.99,0:07:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie escaped from the palace?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.07,0:07:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me straight!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.58,0:07:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't it learn to escape from the beginning?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.45,0:07:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.41,0:07:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You sold the dog at a high price even though you\Nknow it won't stay with anyone else, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.32,0:08:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What a smart plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.68,0:08:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You know me, I'm Heinz, you can't fool me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.06,0:08:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's wrong! I'm not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.60,0:08:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you want to go now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.30,0:08:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.33,0:08:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie... I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.55,0:08:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But I must keep my promise to the Duke!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.41,0:08:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I will definitely be able to recover you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.78,0:08:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.44,0:08:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, come!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.29,0:08:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,John!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.13,0:08:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.76,0:08:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.46,0:08:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.54,0:08:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It will come back quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.20,0:08:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I just agreed with Priscilla's grandfather!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.53,0:08:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You agree with him...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.34,0:08:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.42,0:08:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Priscilla loves dogs a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.97,0:08:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But is it okay to let Lassie go alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.70,0:08:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It will be fine, it will be back soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.83,0:08:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.24,0:08:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,To the mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.26,0:08:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I will help my father!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.48,0:08:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But the mine is closed now...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.20,0:08:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ah!\N- Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.15,0:09:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's moving!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.29,0:09:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I will help you, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.21,0:09:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I must do everything I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.68,0:09:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, manager...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.36,0:09:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,John?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.52,0:09:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...! Kids can't enter here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.64,0:10:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to help you bring out coal!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.59,0:10:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.72,0:10:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! No, get back quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.64,0:10:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- Manager!\N- Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.29,0:10:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let him come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.56,0:10:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll talk to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.93,0:10:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.48,0:10:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.82,0:10:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Father, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.90,0:10:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you help me here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.51,0:10:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, I want to do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.03,0:10:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.60,0:10:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We must drill deeper.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.52,0:10:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I collect samples for each of these rocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.20,0:10:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to dig throuh this soil, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.44,0:10:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,There is one thing you can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.93,0:10:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Use this to collect rock samples.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.64,0:10:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.34,0:10:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us do our best to extract coal!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.90,0:10:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,John!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.31,0:10:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.45,0:10:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This is for Lassie too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.94,0:10:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Father, that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.07,0:11:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ian!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.36,0:11:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.73,0:11:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.43,0:11:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Carraclough, is it reasonable\Nto let your son do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.33,0:11:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No, but this time I have to let him do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.16,0:11:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You will become a pig if you fall!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.44,0:11:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.34,0:12:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.08,0:12:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,My house is full of strange men!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.47,0:12:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,John!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.29,0:12:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.05,0:12:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't come yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.03,0:12:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,John...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.58,0:12:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.47,0:12:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If you run away I will shoot you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.46,0:12:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.06,0:12:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can't make any hole!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.08,0:13:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Be careful, it's hot!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.78,0:13:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.13,0:13:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel a bit strange about this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.53,0:13:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the Duke has something in his mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.36,0:13:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He decided to return to\NScotland all of a sudden!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.15,0:13:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.83,0:13:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's so, Lassie...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.96,0:13:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Could also Lassie...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.88,0:13:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.00,0:13:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to drill without thinking\Nabout other things!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.48,0:13:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to prove to the Duke what we can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.95,0:13:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.98,0:13:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If coal doesn't come out I won't\Nbe able to buy food for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.82,0:13:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, your wife is pregnant, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.94,0:13:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So... If coal doesn't come out, it will die!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.69,0:13:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't even buy milk!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.28,0:13:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is the father's responsibility!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.95,0:13:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- Do your best!\N- Yes!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.47,0:13:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,My responsability...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.90,0:14:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,John!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.28,0:14:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you go to the mine today?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.55,0:14:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.53,0:14:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't played with you lately, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.79,0:14:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,John, will Lassie go to Scotland?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.79,0:14:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.43,0:14:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,My father heard this from some people!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.77,0:14:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Today they will send it with the plane!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.75,0:14:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,They told us there was no need\Nto send food to the dog tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.37,0:14:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that Lassie...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.56,0:14:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, can't we get\NLassie back before it leaves?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.07,0:14:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.43,0:14:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,John!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.21,0:14:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.02,0:14:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We can get Lassie back when coal comes out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.24,0:14:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I have to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.91,0:14:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a lot I have to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.50,0:14:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,John!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.09,0:14:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.56,0:15:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We will send these samples\Nto the laboratory for analysis!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.88,0:15:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.64,0:15:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to know how many layers are displayed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.29,0:15:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,This place is called Old Coal Life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.68,0:15:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Although it is a very old layer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.90,0:15:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}However, when we know\Nthe default age of the layers,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.65,0:15:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}we could find coal more easily!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.29,0:15:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.16,0:15:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow you are better than me in this area!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.60,0:15:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.57,0:15:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I will send it by mail!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.22,0:15:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I count on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.19,0:15:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,John the selfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.32,0:15:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll travel two days by train,\Nit was comfortable in Yorkshire, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.00,0:16:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, Heinz!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.61,0:16:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a long time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.99,0:16:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you brought with you a new animal?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.06,0:16:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.14,0:16:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought it from the remote Yorkshire!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.68,0:16:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,My grandfather ​​really likes dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.39,0:16:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it a good type?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.57,0:16:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, you can see that very soon, Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.93,0:16:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.67,0:16:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.32,0:16:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the boy called John.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.24,0:16:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He is a good boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.25,0:16:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He decided to take responsibility
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.98,0:16:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and give me Lassie without crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.69,0:16:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Priscilla...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.93,0:16:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I strongly acknowledge the will of that boy,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.48,0:17:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,but if the coal doesn't come down,\NLassie will be mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.21,0:17:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It will be yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.14,0:17:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Priscilla!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.22,0:17:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'll be back if I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.86,0:17:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't you think it's rude\Nto reunite John and Lassie
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.56,0:17:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,suddenly after we agreed?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.97,0:17:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}John!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.79,0:17:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Mail!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.69,0:17:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad said I should bring it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.83,0:17:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Please read it quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.51,0:17:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you rush so!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.90,0:17:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,How were the results of the analyzes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.08,0:17:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you rush so!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.70,0:17:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.17,0:17:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We have not succeeded!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.42,0:17:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.24,0:17:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.00,0:17:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Coal is not under that layer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.28,0:17:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a possibility that the result is zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.11,0:17:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It is rare that the result is zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.86,0:17:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't believe!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.77,0:17:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.71,0:17:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- Can't be that...\N- John!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.50,0:18:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lassie...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.04,0:18:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't it be back yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.46,0:18:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,John, be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.57,0:18:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.60,0:18:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,John, please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.70,0:18:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only John...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.73,0:18:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all shocked...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.51,0:18:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.94,0:18:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.73,0:19:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.89,0:19:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,John?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.34,0:19:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,John!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.82,0:19:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Colin and Sandy told me I'd find you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.55,0:19:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,They were sure you are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.93,0:19:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This is your special place!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.84,0:19:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,John, and Colin, and Sandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.00,0:19:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Priscilla...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.07,0:19:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And also Lassie... father...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.34,0:19:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.83,0:19:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I understood, also Lassie...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.84,0:19:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Now... let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.76,0:20:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Outside, others are waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.74,0:20:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Waiting for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.12,0:20:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,John!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.92,0:20:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Sandy...  Colin!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.32,0:20:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,John the fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.62,0:20:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to think about it yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.94,0:20:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Now let's go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.81,0:20:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother is also waiting for us, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.86,0:20:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.73,0:20:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is Lassie inside on such iron sheets?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.50,0:20:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh! Uh... uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.69,0:20:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No, in fact we put these so it won't escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.70,0:20:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Escape?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.63,0:20:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Yes-yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.77,0:20:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the best way I did
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.94,0:20:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,after it escaped from the Yorkshire\Nmansion several times!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.03,0:20:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No, of course it've been trained on this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.80,0:20:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He got a lot of money after selling it to someone\Nelse, and he knew he would run away again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.00,0:20:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I thought of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.10,0:20:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,John couldn't think of something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.55,0:21:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If Lassie is still waiting for John's return,\Nit can't remain silent!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.00,0:21:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It don't want to be patient!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.31,0:21:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't bear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.96,0:21:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,John... even John wants to see\NLassie without a doubt!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.78,0:21:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,My grandfather doesn't understand anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.43,0:21:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh... ah... whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.56,0:21:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.04,0:21:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.54,0:21:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to go to John's place?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.85,0:21:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You can go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.90,0:21:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! Oh-ah-ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.34,0:21:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.63,0:21:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't open it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.83,0:21:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't open the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.33,0:21:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,No, but open it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.99,0:21:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Aah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.55,0:21:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.93,0:21:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Let it go to John!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.78,0:22:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}From faraway Scotland,\NLasie travels back to my home.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.76,0:22:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And without food...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.06,0:22:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lassie chasing unruly dogs.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.85,0:22:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This time it faces the gun!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.33,0:22:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Next episode:\NUNKNOWN PLACES. SEARCH FOR LASSIE{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.70,0:22:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Be sure to watch!{\i0}
